He comes off to me as a different person sometimes and though I think there are many sides to him just like any other person, I can’t come up with a stable image of who he is in my mind. body:
“i had a very wide stance. someone took a photo of me and i was like-“

“oh, phil—“

(danandphilgames— ‘who should we date? dan and phil play heart ♡ throb) drawn by: @existentialhouseplant aka arthur :)

i hope you like this lil’ drawing of the lovely humans @amazingphil and @danielhowell !

i haven’t drawn for fun in a hot minute so i’m trying to get back into it. i’m going to work on some more d & p drawings (maybe paintings too if i’m feeling WILD). i’m going to draw some more iconic video moments and try to come up with some original dan and phil art ideas.

also, i think i spent more time on dan’s mouth than the rest of the drawing.

i hope you all are having a wonderful day!

please leave credit ♡
